### User Registration and Login API Testing

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login with existing user
POST http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get all users (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get user by ID (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update user (requires JWT token)
PUT http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "username": "johndoe_updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123"
}

###

### Delete user (requires JWT token)
DELETE http://localhost:5163/api/Auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get all products (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5163/api/Products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get product by ID (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5163/api/Products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create a new product (requires JWT token)
POST http://localhost:5163/api/Products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "High performance laptop",
  "price": 1299.99
}

###

### Update a product (requires JWT token)
PUT http://localhost:5163/api/Products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Updated Laptop",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": 1399.99
}

###

### Delete a product (requires JWT token)
DELETE http://localhost:5163/api/Products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
